Class XYDataPointObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • helpers.XYDataPointObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class XYDataPointObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A generic key/value class used for a few different functions but was written to store RBNB data where x is the timestamp and y is the datapoint.
    Author:
    jdk85
    See Also:
    SegaDataRequestServlet, DataFetchHelper, RBNBChannelObject, RequestFormServlet, Serialized Form
